Absolutely! You can now run your agent with one click or one command directly inside Antigravity:

Option 1: The "Slash Command" (Easiest)
Whenever you want to start your server, just type this in our chat:

/run

I have set up a Workflow for you. When you type /run, I will automatically:

Kill any stuck servers.
Fix your dependencies.
Launch the AI Agent for you.
Option 2: Double-Click in Windows
If you are outside of this chat, you can simply double-click the file named 
START_AGENT.bat
 in your project folder. It will do exactly the same thing.

Why this is better:
You don't need to remember commands like python app.py.
You don't need to worry about "Port already in use" errors.
Everything is handled for you automatically.
